{"mode":2,"scripts":[{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"近くの飛行場と航空基地が重桜の航空隊に襲われたわ！","actor":201230,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":-1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"……ちぃ、小賢しい真似を……","dir":-1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"actor":205060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ウェールズ、それと……","actor":204020,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"わかってる。ユニオンの連中も襲われたわ。……重桜め、結構やる気のようね…","actor":205060,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":-1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"うん、これじゃユニオンへの援軍要請は無理ね…","actor":204020,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"だから？最初から期待できない盟友が襲われたぐらいで動揺して…あんたらしくないわ、「レパルスお姉さん」。","actor":205060,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":-1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"「お姉さん」はいいから！この艦隊はウェールズがリーダーでしょ？もうみんな「お姉さん」「お姉さん」って鳥肌になっちゃったよ……","actor":204020,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"まあ心配することはない。例え航空支援がなくても、重桜の航空隊なんて私のHACSさえあれば恐れることはないさ。","actor":205060,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":-1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"ずっと中立を装ってたユニオンの連中もこれでいい加減気づくね。","actor":205060,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":-1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"うん、それもそうだよね……","actor":204020,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"いずれにしても、基地のみんなには我がロイヤルの栄光を持って助けねば。ちょうどいい加減待つのにも飽きたし、レパルス、あんたは大丈夫？","actor":205060,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":-1},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"これぐらい大丈夫よ！伊達に艦歴が長いわけじゃないわ！多分じっとしてたから変なこと考えるようになっちゃったね…","actor":204020,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"よし！全艦単縦陣、前進開始！――「喧嘩を買いにいくわよ！」","actor":204020,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":0},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"これでこそ私の知っているレパルスね。では……少し腕鳴らしに行こうか！","actor":205060,"nameColor":"#a9f548","shake":{"number":3,"speed":1},"dir":-1}],"id":"TACT10001","once":true}